snippet.title: Raji: An Ancient Epic Enhanced Edition - Trailer
snippet.description:
Raji: An Ancient Epic is an action-adventure game set in Ancient India. Raji, a young girl chosen by the gods, will stand against the demonic invasion into the human realm. Her destiny is to rescue her younger brother and face the demon lord Mahabalasura.

For more on Raji: An Ancient Epic, follow the game on social media on the following channels.
